					PRIVACY NOTICE


OUR COMMITMENT TO PRIVACY

	Certain personally identifiable information received by Special Education Solutions, Inc is used in datasets of our applications, specifically SpEdFast and Equity Squared.  Our commitment to the privacy of this information is very important to us.  Our web-based applications, which are developed for centralized management of student files, are subject to the strictest protection currently available.

THE INFORMATION WE COLLECT

	This notice applies to all information collected or submitted to Special Education Solutions, Inc by the purchasing School District for the development of datasets of centralized management files.  Any personally identifiable information collected is not disclosed, divulged or available, either directly or indirectly, to any third party without the express, written consent of the purchasing School District.  

OUR COMMITMENT TO DATA SECURITY

	To prevent unauthorized access, maintain data accuracy and ensure the correct use of the information, we have put in place appropriate physical, electronic and managerial procedures to safeguard and secure the information we collect.  Special Education Solutions applications are secure with 128-bit encryption.  The connections use TLS 1.2 and are encrypted and authenticated using AES_128_GCM and uses ECDHE_RSA as the key exchange mechanism.


Affiliated Business Disclosure
Special Education Solutions, Inc. has a business agreement in place with Clever, Inc for data integration services.  For data security information, please visit https://clever.com/security .


HOW TO CONTACT US 

	Should you have other questions or concerns about the privacy policy, please call us at 888-549-6123 or send us an email at support@sescompliance.com
